   * runtime, this is the only case. In the automatic runtime, this is called
   * as a fallback in some situations.
   *
   * Example:
   * <div a={1} key={2}>Hello{x}</div>
   * becomes
   * React.createElement('div', {a: 1, key: 2}, "Hello", x)
